## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/ogcae/fuero
cd fuero

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run tests
python -m pytest

# Run examples
fuero run examples/hello.fuero
fuero run examples/math_demo.fuero
fuero run examples/string_demo.fuero
```

